.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
Manage the saved searches stored in this database.
If you try to add a query with a name that already exists, it will be
replaced.
.sp
Syntax for adding:
.sp
calibredb \fBsaved_searches\fP add search_name search_expression
.sp
Syntax for removing:
